---
source: tests/conformance/query_v1_matrix.rs
assertion: ee.query.v1 query-file tag filters select and exclude memories deterministically
schema:
  query_file: ee.query.v1
  filters: ee.query.filters.tags.v1
contracts:
  - tags.require requires all listed tags
  - tags.requireAny accepts any listed tag
  - tags.exclude removes matching candidates
  - combined tag filters have deterministic behavior and stable ordering
  - wrong tag object or element types fail with stable machine errors
  - empty tag arrays are documented no-op filters rather than hidden fallback
evidence:
  - tests/conformance/query_v1_matrix.rs::matrix_tags_require_only
  - tests/conformance/query_v1_matrix.rs::matrix_tags_require_any
  - tests/conformance/query_v1_matrix.rs::matrix_tags_exclude
  - tests/conformance/query_v1_matrix.rs::matrix_tags_combined_filters
  - tests/conformance/query_v1_matrix.rs::matrix_error_tags_wrong_type_array
